Barb almost goes off or cwcchat_0001.wmv is a short audio recording from a Skype chat between Chris and Sarah May. As the title implies, the leaked chat involves Barb almost freaking out on Chris due to him going against her suggestions of not talking to random strangers on the Internet.

The creation date of the video file was 19 March 2009. However, since Sarah revealed she was a troll on the 4th of March, it is unlikely the conversation took place on the same day. This audio recording has not been revealed until Statustjej leaked it on YouTube on 24 October 2025 over a decade later.
